Here's a full breakdown of the Playbook service architecture.

Playbook Service Architecture
Overview
The system is split across 4 runtime processes that communicate via RabbitMQ and Socket.IO:

Service	Port	Role
Playbook-service	5000	Workflow engine, DB owner
API-Gateway	4000	Auth proxy to Playbook-service
backend	—	Socket.IO relay, alarm publishing
frontend	—	React designer + live monitoring
System Flow Diagram

